elements.text: Workflow Explanation: 1) Rate limiting check (1000 RPS) 2) Provider selection (weighted: P1:70%, P2:20%, P3:10%) 3) Circuit breaker check (skip if in cooldown) 4) Simulate provider call (latency + error rate) 5) Mark failure & apply exponential backoff if error 6) Return response (200/429/502) 7) Record metrics (Prometheus)
